<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>My Reading Corner</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .section-title {
      color: #007bff;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .box {
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid #007bff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #343a40;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>My Reading Corner</h1>
    <p>Learning how to use Bootstrap badges</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="section-title">My Reading List</h2>

    <div class="box">
      <h3>Story Books <span class="badge badge-primary">8</span></h3>
      <p>I love reading story books every evening.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
      <h3>Comics <span class="badge badge-success">5</span></h3>
      <p>Comics are fun and full of colourful pictures.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
      <h3>Poems <span class="badge badge-warning">3</span></h3>
      <p>I enjoy reading short poems and rhymes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
      <h3>Magazines <span class="badge badge-danger">2</span></h3>
      <p>Magazines help me learn new facts and ideas.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Reading Progress</h2>

    <p>Books Read <span class="badge badge-dark">15</span></p>
    <p>Pages Completed <span class="badge badge-info">120</span></p>
    <p>New Words Learned <span class="badge badge-secondary">45</span></p>

  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid footer">
    <p>Made with Bootstrap — Badge Practice</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
